dude, a few years ago in the middle of the day on a saturday, there was a young girl just passed out on the ground dressed up by the state of illinois building on the lasalle and randolph side.

i never seen something so tragic. cops were there literally in a moment or so, but just walking by no one around and she's face down,

i'll never forget it. and cops see this all the time.

it hurt when i saw that and i knew, some combo of either alcohol and / or drugs.

~peace
